descp2: Specifies the attributes for nodes in the generated visualization. node_attrs is a dictionary of Graphviz attribute names and values. For example: node_attrs={"shape":"oval","fixedsize":"false"}   will use oval shape for nodes and allow variable sized nodes in the visualization.
